category: Accessibility
requires: libaudio2 libdotconf1.0_0 libespeak1 libgcc1 libglib2.0_0 libsndfile1 libspeechd2
sdesc: "Speech synthesis interface (server and client apps)"
ldesc: "The Speech Dispatcher project provides a device independent 
layer for speech synthesis. It provides a simple interface for client 
applications (applications, that want to speak) as well as for device 
driver modules (the different speech synthesizers)."
